name: Trick or Treat - Haunted Pumpkin
description:
The pumpkins began to appear in the middle of the night. No one knew exactly what or why they appeared. All they knew is that the wailing coming from within kept them up at night, shaking in their covers.

One brave recipient picked up their pumpkin, and upon examining, saw the numbers "11 1 21" carved in the bottom. Unfortunately, he didn't get to ponder too much more, as he was immediately killed in a freak bolt of lightening. 

Coincidence? 
Perhaps.
What fate will become of those who hold this pumpkin in their possession?
